short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A browser extension that automatically syncs your LinkedIn Connections with SmallWorld.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Seamlessly sync your LinkedIn connections to SmallWorld.ai and rate the strength of your relationships without leaving LinkedIn, giving the team insight into where you may be able to help.

Key Features:
	•	Sync LinkedIn connections automatically to SmallWorld.ai
	•	Rate the strength of your relationships directly on LinkedIn
	•	Stay updated with new connections and job changes
	•	Works on Chrome, Microsoft Edge, Opera, Brave, and more
